So many core memories made 💛 Since having kids over 8 years ago, we’ve only been away twice for about 24 hours and one of those trips was for work. We’re so grateful for all of the family memories we get to make with our kids, but man did it feel good to just get to be us for a few days and do things we love together.

I’ll be honest though, by the last two days all we could think of was the kids. We took pictures of so many dogs, cool trees, and fun graffiti, because we wished we could share part of the adventure with them. Who knows, maybe next time we’re in NYC they’ll be with us 🤞🏻

#newyorkcity #nyctrip #momanddad #grownuptime
